name: The Virtual Palace HP and Respawn Test HTML
name_original: The Virtual Palace HP and Respawn Test HTML
description:
this is only a test, i used a different game engine for this one and i kinda wanted to see if it would be better if i swapped to this one instead, its a little bit less complex to me, so i feel a bit more comfortable using it. i exported the project to here because its been a while since i did anything  so i decided to push myself to finish something, even if this is as basic as a prototype can get. I will do my absolute best to get a good quality demo build finished soon.

made with gdevelop and some of its default assets.
